WEBVTT

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:10.000
My name is Kylie, and I'm so thankful for Gateway Family Chiropractic.
I've been dealing with severe stomach pain and headaches for over eight years.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:18.000
I went to a bunch of doctors, and they couldn't really diagnose me with something specific.
Then I went to Gateway, and they helped me figure it out.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:25.000
They helped start to help my stomach get better.
At night, I would twist and turn, and then it wouldn't stop hurting.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:33.000
Then I would just start throwing up, and it was getting to the point
where I wouldn't go to school for a week because it hurt so bad.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:42.000
It was interfering with sleeping, resting, my sports,
and just everyday life.

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:49.000
When I first started seeing the results, I was excited
that I could start enjoying volleyball and sleeping better.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:57.000
I could start actually doing things I enjoyed
without the pain of my stomach interfering with it.

00:00:57.000 --> 00:01:04.000
After two visits, they started to help me,
and my stomach started to feel better.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:13.000
The pain was starting to relieve.
They can figure out every single place that hurts, and they just do it so perfectly.

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:21.000
I'm just doing better through school because I can focus on school
and not have to worry about my stomach.

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:26.000
I'm Kylie, and I go camping, I play volleyball,
I focus on school, and I do activities with friends.

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:30.000
I got to eat, and I can do that now
because my stomach pain is basically gone because of Gateway.
